OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FWood recovered from a project to
OL,7,Frestore Birnbeck Pier in Weston-super-
OL,8,FMare will be transformed into handmade
OL,9,Ffurniture.
OL,11,FNorth Somerset Council has announced
OL,12,Fthe salvaged wood that cannot be
OL,13,Freused on the Grade II* structure will
OL,14,Fbe turned into items and sold to fund
OL,15,Fmaintenance of the site.
OL,17,FSomerset Wood Recycling will give the
OL,18,Fwood a new lease of life by turning it
OL,19,Finto items for sale at a new shop in
OL,20,Fthe Pier Master's Cottage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
