FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FAll income generated from their sale
OL,7,Fwill be spent on the daily maintenance
OL,8,Fof the site.
OL,10,FThe council says the initiative has
OL,11,Fbeen made possible thanks to funding
OL,12,Ffrom The National Lottery Heritage
OL,13,FFund.
OL,15,FSomerset Wood Recycling is a Community
OL,16,FInterest Company, which means their
OL,17,Ffocus is to provide community benefit
OL,18,Frather than profit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
