OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FThey provide training and employment
OL,7,Fopportunities in woodworking,
OL,8,Fcarpentry, recycling, and general life
OL,9,Fskills for local people.
OL,11,FAs part of the project, it will offer
OL,12,Fa six-month placement in carpentry and
OL,13,Fwoodworking to four trainees.
OL,15,FAt least two of these placements will
OL,16,Fbe offered to young people through the
OL,17,Fcouncil's Youth Justice Service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
