PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FTom Palmer, director of Somerset Wood
OL,7,FRecycling, said: "We're excited to be
OL,8,Fworking with North Somerset Council,
OL,9,Fand their appointed contractor
OL,10,FMackley, on the Birnbeck Pier project.
OL,12,F"We're looking forward to finding a
OL,13,Fnew purpose for timber reclaimed from
OL,14,Fthe pier; creating employment and
OL,15,Ftraining opportunities for local
OL,16,Fpeople while making a little bit of
OL,17,FWeston's heritage available for people
OL,18,Fto own."
OL,26,@oD@ROUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
