PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FCouncillor Mark Canniford, North
OL,7,FSomerset Council's cabinet member
OL,8,Fresponsible for the Birnbeck Project,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This partnership forms part of
OL,10,Four comprehensive community engagement
OL,11,Fplan for the project, which has been
OL,12,Fmade possible thanks to funding from
OL,13,FThe National Lottery Heritage Fund.
OL,15,F"Not only does this enable us to
OL,16,Frepurpose the wood from our much-loved
OL,17,F'old pier', by working with Somerset
OL,18,FWood Recycling we're able to get the
OL,19,Fcommunity involved with the process
OL,20,Ftoo.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,F"On top of that, the money raised will
OL,7,Fgo towards maintaining the pier after
OL,8,Four restoration project has finished.
OL,10,F"It's a win-win all round! Well done
OL,11,Fto our Heritage and Design team for
OL,12,Fmaking this happen. I look forward to
OL,13,Fseeing the results."
OL,15,FMetalwork recovered from the pier
OL,16,Fstructure, including seat backs and
OL,17,Flamp posts, is being recovered and
OL,18,Ftested.
OL,26,@uD@TO]
