PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773765945
OL,3,CWood from Birnbeck Pier to be
OL,4,Ctransformed into furniture
OL,6,FAll sound material will be cleaned and
OL,7,Freused. Pieces that are too damaged or
OL,8,Fhave been lost will be replaced.
OL,10,FThe long-awaited restoration of
OL,11,FBirnbeck Pier started earlier this
OL,12,Fyear, and will cost nearly #23
OL,13,Fmillion. North Somerset Council says
OL,14,Fit could be completed by next summer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
